{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/pidfile"]}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PIDFile","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PIDFile"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:15SpooktacularKit7PIDFileO","symbolKind":"enum","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"title":"PIDFile"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Type-Properties","title":"Type Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/fileName"]},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Type-Methods","title":"Type Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/isProcessAlive(_:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/isRunning(bundleURL:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/read(from:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/remove(from:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/terminate(bundleURL:gracePeriod:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/write(to:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/writeAndEnsureCapacity(bundleURL:vmDirectory:)"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PIDFile","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"